beer.beer_description:
For the people who reckon that all Hazys & New England IPAs taste the same!
Listen here, mate…Shhhhhh! This one’s full of experimentation and surprises.
Implementing the uber-concentrated Citra & Mosaic Lupomax®, a hop that doesn’t even have a name yet (HBC 586) and a combo of barley, wheat, spelt
AND oats, this is a one of one. Hoppy, soft, pillowy and salivatingly juicy.

items.badge_description: It takes the perfect amount of light, the right framing and a touch of creative love to get the perfect picture of your brew. Now it’s time to drink it! That’s 165 check-ins with a photo.

You may not be able to see through the haze, but that juicy, hoppy goodness goes down smooth. What started as a trend is here to stay. That's 115 different beers with the style of IPA - New England / Hazy, Pale Ale - New England / Hazy, IPA - Milkshake, or Pale Ale - Milkshake. Try 5 more for Level 24!
